## üß≠ Notes
- VLANs are segmented with separate DHCP scopes.
- Downstream Unifi switches should match tagging logic for proper traffic handling.
- AdGuard Home is reachable at `10.10.10.11`, serving DNS filtering for Docker VLAN clients.
